290
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:17,050
[Beiyao Entertainment]

291
00:15:17,050 --> 00:15:17,770
Director Lu.
[Beiyao Entertainment]

292
00:15:17,770 --> 00:15:17,810
[Beiyao Entertainment]

293
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:20,920
I'll thank you on behalf of Nan Chu.

294
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,640
Thank you for giving her this chance.

295
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,770
I'll treat you to dinner next time.

296
00:15:25,370 --> 00:15:26,170
Okay, bye.

297
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,020
It's done.

298
00:15:32,930 --> 00:15:33,900
Boss, do you think

299
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:36,630
