303
00:15:41,290 --> 00:15:42,130
Take it one step at a time.

304
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:45,780
Boss,

305
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,010
do you think

306
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:49,520
Nan Chu

307
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:52,000
is really not up to this job?

308
00:15:56,070 --> 00:15:57,040
Give it a try.

309
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:59,260
If we wait any longer,

310
00:15:59,260 --> 00:16:01,280
Flaming Youth's hype

311
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:02,540
will completely die down.

312
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:04,680
We'll really be unable to do anything by then.

313
00:16:04,890 --> 00:16:05,350
Yes.

314
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,000
You know what?

315
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,640
I always dreamed of you.

316
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:11,820
But you always ran too fast,

317
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,920
so I could only see your back

318
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:15,310
and couldn't catch up...

319
00:16:15,310 --> 00:16:15,770
Stop.

320
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:23,160
Get ready for the next scene.

321
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:24,630
Take her to change into her outfit.

322
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,390
Okay.

323
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:26,140
Let's go.

324
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:27,110
Go get changed.

325
00:16:37,690 --> 00:16:38,990
What kind of makeup

326
00:16:39,250 --> 00:16:40,460
would you like?

327
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,350
Nan Chu.

328
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:42,900
You have lines this time

329
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:43,820
and quite a few of them.

330
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,000
I'll give yo a prettier makeup.

