00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:50,710
[Lin Luxiao]
[Time]

332
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:51,680
[Nan Chu]

333
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:54,410
I passed the audition. How is it going over there?
[Nan Chu]

334
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:55,880
[Nan Chu]

335
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:06,800
[Lin Luxiao]

336
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:09,320
Something suddenly came up so I'm on my way back to the brigade.
[Lin Luxiao]

337
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:09,990
[Lin Luxiao]

338
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:11,500
Yang is in low spirits,
[Lin Luxiao]

339
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,800
so I'm quite worried.
[Lin Luxiao]

340
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:15,910
[Lin Luxiao]

341
00:18:33,020 --> 00:18:33,570
Hello?

342
00:18:33,780 --> 00:18:34,240
What's wrong?

343
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,370
Lin, come here now!

344
00:18:35,370 --> 00:18:36,210
Something bad happened!

345
00:18:36,210 --> 00:18:37,430
Yang wants to jump off the building!

346
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:37,940
What?

347
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:39,070
Yang wants to jump off a building!

348
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,040
Don't do anything rash.

349
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,250
Keep him calm.

350
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:41,880
I'll be right there.

351
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:39,420
Comrade.

352
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:41,160
Stop drinking, comrade.

353
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:42,320
Calm down.

354
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:43,740
Come over here first.

355
00:19:43,850 --> 00:19:45,600
Whatever it is, we can talk about it.

356
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:47,740
There's nothing we can't overcome.

357
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,300
Don't take it too hard.

358
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,220
I'll leave it to you.

359
00:19:59,710 --> 00:20:00,210
Yang.

360
00:20:00,210 --> 00:20:01,050
Get the rescue air cushion ready.

361
00:20:01,050 --> 00:20:02,270
Time is tight.

362
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:02,820
Hurry up.

363
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:06,390
Yang.

364
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:07,980
Stop drinking.

365
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:10,920
Come back with us.

366
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:13,530
Don't make things difficult for us.

367
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:14,160
Okay?

368
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:43,430
Yang.

369
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:48,260
We've been brothers for so many years

370
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:51,200
and been through thick and thin for so many years.

371
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,770
How many life-and-death situations have we been through?

372
00:20:54,770 --> 00:20:56,360
You've never once been afraid.

373
00:20:58,550 --> 00:21:00,650
Why can't you make it today?

374
00:21:01,780 --> 00:21:04,090
Why can't you get past it today?

375
00:21:18,620 --> 00:21:19,460
Instructor Yang.

376
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:21,230
We'll step back.

377
00:21:21,690 --> 00:21:22,570
We won't move.

378
00:21:22,570 --> 00:21:24,630
I know the procedure better than any of you.

379
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:26,900
Instructor Yang.

380
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:27,700
We won't move.

381
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:29,040
You remember Sun Meng, right?

382
00:21:29,290 --> 00:21:30,050
Retreat.

383
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:31,140
We'll step back.

384
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:35,260
Yu.

385
00:21:37,230 --> 00:21:38,360
I'm not afraid of death.

386
00:21:43,570 --> 00:21:44,920
Neither am I

387
00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:47,350
trying to make things difficult for everyone.

388
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:52,640
I just figured it out.

389
00:21:58,730 --> 00:22:00,660
I should have died at South Bay Harbor

390
00:22:02,220 --> 00:22:04,110
and sacrificed my life at the most worthy time.

391
00:22:29,100 --> 00:22:30,060
In my life,

392
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,210
I've only done one job.

393
00:22:36,780 --> 00:22:38,130
This is the only job I can do.

394
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,320
But now,

395
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:45,980
I can't even do it anymore.

396
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:47,870
Tell me.

397
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,600
What's the point

398
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:52,410
of living for me?

399
00:23:00,980 --> 00:23:01,980
No job,

400
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:04,500
no life,

401
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,820
and no dignity.

402
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:15,630
Brothers.

403
00:23:18,990 --> 00:23:21,560
If you still regard me as your instructor,

404
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,080
go back.

405
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,020
Leave me with some dignity.

406
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:30,580
I also want to

407
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,060
leave a good impression to you.

408
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:38,100
[Beixun City Fire and Rescue Brigade]

409
00:23:41,630 --> 00:23:44,280
[Beixun City Fire and Rescue Brigade]

410
00:23:48,310 --> 00:23:49,060
Excuse me.

411
00:23:49,530 --> 00:23:50,320
Sorry to bother you.

412
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:52,680
I'm looking for a female fire control operator with the surname Li

413
00:23:53,050 --> 00:23:54,900
who often contacts Heping Road Special Division Station.

414
00:23:55,530 --> 00:23:56,500
Instructor Yang.

415
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:58,260
You mustn't do anything stupid.

416
00:23:58,260 --> 00:23:59,230
You always told me

417
00:23:59,230 --> 00:24:01,120
you'd help to turn me into an excellent firefighter.

418
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:03,220
I still have many questions to ask you.

419
00:24:03,470 --> 00:24:05,070
Can you come up and answer me?

420
00:24:05,490 --> 00:24:06,660
Don't do anything stupid.

421
00:24:08,090 --> 00:24:08,890
Yes, Yang.

422
00:24:10,230 --> 00:24:12,040
We still have a lot of things to do together.

423
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:14,730
Right.

424
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:16,070
It's here...

425
00:24:16,070 --> 00:24:16,870
It's nearby.

426
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:19,560
I think it's that building.

427
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:20,480
That community.

428
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:21,530
Have you forgotten?

429
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:23,710
We saved a little boy then.

430
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:25,480
He told us

431
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:28,040
to visit him every festival,

432
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:29,260
right?

433
00:24:30,220 --> 00:24:31,900
Speaking of which, I remember it now.

434
00:24:32,490 --> 00:24:33,500
Then, we...

435
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:35,050
I observed just now

436
00:24:35,470 --> 00:24:37,150
that there is a window below the instructor.

437
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:38,620
I think we can go to the floor below

438
00:24:39,130 --> 00:24:40,300
and rescue him from behind.

439
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,440
We can try it.

440
00:24:42,320 --> 00:24:43,240
Don't.

441
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,380
Instructor Yang is experienced.

442
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:46,060
He must be able to see that position.

443
00:24:47,150 --> 00:24:48,580
We must not provoke him now.

444
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,890
Otherwise, the consequences will be unimaginable.

445
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:53,240
The position where the instructor's sitting at is too tricky.

446
00:24:53,490 --> 00:24:54,460
What do you think we should do then?

447
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,470
Yang.

448
00:24:55,470 --> 00:24:56,390
You...

449
00:24:56,390 --> 00:24:57,310
You can't do this.

450
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,240
You have to come down first.

451
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,370
How is it going?

452
00:24:59,370 --> 00:25:00,800
Pay me back the money for the beer

453
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:01,890
that you owe me first.

454
00:25:02,810 --> 00:25:03,570
Yang.

455
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,170
What are you doing?

456
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:06,720
Come over first

457
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:07,940
and we can talk about everything slowly.

458
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:14,360
I know you're suffering inside.

459
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,340
Tell us about it.

460
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:17,600
For many things, if you say it out,

461
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:18,610
you'll feel better.

462
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:22,390
How about this?

463
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:23,650
Come over here

464
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,240
and I'll drink with you.

465
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:27,130
Then this will be over, okay?

466
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:33,980
Yang.

467
00:25:34,150 --> 00:25:34,900
What are you doing?

468
00:25:35,530 --> 00:25:36,410
Get out of there now.

469
00:25:36,790 --> 00:25:37,340
Hurry!

470
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,220
Yang!

471
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:38,680
Don't come over.

472
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:39,690
You are a firefighter.

473
00:25:39,690 --> 00:25:40,700
Is this appropriate?

474
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:42,170
Hurry up.

475
00:25:42,550 --> 00:25:43,130
Yang.

476
00:25:43,130 --> 00:25:44,650
Luxiao is here too.

477
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:45,950
Stop resisting.

478
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:47,630
Come up.

479
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:49,520
Come back with us.

480
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:49,980
Okay?

481
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:53,380
I want to go back too.

482
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:56,780
But do you think...

483
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:00,480
I still can go back?

484
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:06,150
Since

485
00:26:07,030 --> 00:26:07,960
everyone is here,

486
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:10,980
today,

487
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:16,400
let's say a proper goodbye here.

488
00:26:20,390 --> 00:26:21,230
Don't...

489
00:26:22,030 --> 00:26:22,700
Wait.

490
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:24,800
We don't agree to your way of saying goodbye like this.

491
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:26,310
Look at everyone.

492
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,650
Everyone is watching.

493
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:29,250
Do you want them

494
00:26:29,250 --> 00:26:30,550
to just watch their instructor

495
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:31,850
jump off the building?

496
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:35,590
Then what else do you want from me?

497
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,370
What else do you want from me?

498
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:42,900
I don't want to admit it,

499
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:48,020
but I'm useless now.

500
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:51,000
I really tried.

501
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:52,220
I tried to persist!

502
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:53,480
I tried to fight against it!

503
00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:00,410
But I really can't persist anymore.

504
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,820
I can't take it anymore.

505
00:27:07,130 --> 00:27:07,850
Yang.

506
00:27:09,950 --> 00:27:11,330
I know you feel bad.

507
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,640
But we are all here.

508
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:14,990
A group of brothers

509
00:27:14,990 --> 00:27:15,870
is all here with you...

510
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:16,620
Don't come near me!

511
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:19,020
Fine.

512
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,240
I won't go over.

513
00:27:20,610 --> 00:27:21,830
You are a firefighter.

514
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:23,180
You know this procedure

515
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,560
better than anyone else.

516
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,410
And you are an instructor.

517
00:27:27,250 --> 00:27:28,260
You're good

518
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:29,560
with thinking things through too.

519
00:27:30,690 --> 00:27:32,330
I know it's hard to save you

520
00:27:32,670 --> 00:27:33,550
and it's useless to persuade you.

521
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:36,280
But we have to persuade you today.

522
00:27:37,250 --> 00:27:39,050
Because you're our brother.

523
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:43,630
Lin.

524
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:49,300
I'm very calm

525
00:27:50,390 --> 00:27:51,150
and rational now.

526
00:27:53,460 --> 00:27:54,590
Do you remember

527
00:27:56,730 --> 00:27:57,570
what I told you

528
00:27:58,960 --> 00:28:00,260
that year

529
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,570
when you were tormenting yourself crazily

530
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:05,050
on the sports ground?

531
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:07,480
I told you that this obstacle

532
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:12,310
can only be overcome by yourself.

533
00:28:13,150 --> 00:28:14,750
No one else can help you,

534
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,770
including me.

535
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,760
But now,

536
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:24,160
I don't even have my legs.

537
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,540
How can I cross this obstacle?

538
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,320
You've thought everything through?

539
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:30,120
Let me tell you.

540
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,730
Yijiu and Shiquan are watching.

541
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,950
What kind of role model are you?

542
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:36,800
How will they grow up in the future?

543
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:40,710
You've been working as a firefighter for so many years.

544
00:28:41,670 --> 00:28:42,220
For so many years,

545
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:43,310
you also said that you can't do anything

546
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:44,570
except firefighting.

547
00:28:45,910 --> 00:28:47,090
What are you doing now?

548
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,360
If you just jump today,

549
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:52,210
you'll be the biggest joke of the firefighting team.

550
00:28:52,210 --> 00:28:53,050
Listen.

551
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:56,200
You'll be ruining the reputation of the entire nation's firefighters.

552
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,460
You'll be a disgrace!

553
00:28:58,770 --> 00:28:59,560
You also said

554
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:01,790
that one should be mentally prepared

555
00:29:02,210 --> 00:29:03,890
from the moment they enter the firefighting industry.

556
00:29:04,690 --> 00:29:06,070
We're all mentally prepared.

557
00:29:06,910 --> 00:29:08,300
What did you prepare?

558
00:29:09,850 --> 00:29:11,370
What are you trying to show us?

559
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:14,470
Are you trying to tell all firefighters

560
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:16,830
that the only way to face pain

561
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:18,550
is to commit suicide?

562
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,230
Yang.

563
00:29:29,130 --> 00:29:31,060
Do you think death is easy?

564
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:36,100
I don't want to do this either,

565
00:29:36,980 --> 00:29:40,090
but I don't want to be a burden to everyone.

566
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:44,420
Even for the simple task of going to the toilet,

567
00:29:44,420 --> 00:29:45,720
I need someone to help me.

568
00:29:48,530 --> 00:29:49,160
Yang.

569
00:29:50,050 --> 00:29:51,470
I know it's not easy for you.

570
00:29:52,610 --> 00:29:53,150
I know.

571
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:56,260
We can't understand how you feel either.

572
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,110
Like you said,

573
00:29:59,450 --> 00:30:00,420
we can't help you.

574
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:01,810
I admit it.

575
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:05,420
But we can accompany you.

576
00:30:07,390 --> 00:30:08,270
These brothers

577
00:30:08,650 --> 00:30:09,740
